  "content": "\n<p>Image gallery is a flexible container for displaying images in grid, masonry, or gallery layouts with lightbox support.</p>\n<h2 id=\"header-image-gallery-example\">Gallery option</h2>\n<image-gallery mode=\"gallery\" accent-color=\"grey\" active-index=\"0\"><img src=\"https://picsum.photos/400/300\" alt=\"Sample image 1\"><img src=\"https://picsum.photos/400/500\" alt=\"Sample image 2\"><img src=\"https://picsum.photos/400/400\" alt=\"Sample image 3\"></image-gallery>\n<h2 id=\"header-image-gallery-example\">Grid option</h2>\n<image-gallery accent-color=\"grey\" mode=\"grid\" active-index=\"0\" _hax-state=\"\">  <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/400/300\" alt=\"Sample image 1\">\n  <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/400/500\" alt=\"Sample image 2\">\n  <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/400/400\" alt=\"Sample image 3\">\n</image-gallery>\n<h2 id=\"header-image-gallery-example\">Masonry option</h2>\n<image-gallery accent-color=\"grey\" mode=\"masonry\" active-index=\"0\" _hax-state=\"\">    <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/400/300\" alt=\"Sample image 1\">\n\n    <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/400/500\" alt=\"Sample image 2\">\n\n    <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/400/400\" alt=\"Sample image 3\">\n\n</image-gallery>\n"
}